### 3. Logging, Metrics & Alarm Infrastructure (The Safety Net)

To transition MEP-light™ away from "pilot purgatory" and establish reliable runtime governance, the physical layer deploys an structured **observability pipeline**:

#### 3.1 Structured JSON Logging
All system activities, calculations, and multi-agent loops are written as structured, machine-readable JSON logs.

