*   Deploy localized **PostgreSQL** schema to handle companies, user sessions, market matrices, and diagnostic metrics.
*   Configure the OAuth client and endpoints with Google Identity.

#### Phase 2: RAG & Calculation APIs (Weeks 3–4)
*   Inject F&B regulatory databases and Middle East export guidelines into a localized **pgvector** container.
*   Program the mathematical scoring backend using FastAPI, implementing inverted scores, categorical metrics, and the custom SME weighting models.
*   Set up automated **pytest** scripts inside `/tests` using the Golden Scenario data (Somayeh F&B / Kashkam) to verify logic gates.

#### Phase 3: Auth Integration & Operational Spaces (Weeks 5–6)
*   Enforce JWT authorization middleware on the back-end API routes, assigning RBAC scopes (`Viewer`, `Consultant`, `Administrator`).
*   Bind the UI frontend state transitions to the FSM.
*   Integrate the serverless PDF-compilation service using ReportLab to export dynamic strategic reports.
*   Build out the **Entry Readiness Workspace** (Product Prep) components for regulatory compliance and product localization.

#### Phase 4: Observability, QA & Cloud Launch (Week 7)
*   Deploy the JSON logging, metrics, and high-priority certain-guardrail alerts.
*   Verify all system components against the automated Golden Evaluation datasets.
*   Activate the **`cloudrun-mcp`** server in Antigravity to build and deploy the production codebase directly to Google Cloud Run.

